Beth,<br>
I second the words of encouragement from the others on this site who have shared their experiences as well as Edward Ramons words of wisdom to not drown yourself in the process.<br><br>
The Vietnam Vet Home page at www.vietvet.org has links to other supports.  From that page comes a link to Patience Mason, the wife of a veteran and  the Editor of the Post-Traumatic Gazette.  May I suggest that if you haven't already been to her site that you take a peek.          http://www.patiencepress.com<br><br>

